Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:08.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共感も栄光も賞賛も欲しがるのは野暮ってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:11.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}正体不明の引力が常識を無に帰す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:13.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}引き金を引いてしまうから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:18.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}冗談じゃねえよ Phantom's begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:20.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,500)\blur2\be1}嘘にまみれきって蜃気楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:23.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}心まで霞んで蜃気楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:26.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善々悪々も審議不能になる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:30.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全部嫌になった　それさえも幸せな結末だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:35.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}だめだ　そんな悲しいこと言うな　まだ世界は生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:37.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}君が泣いてたって生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:40.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}だからこの空の先を見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:45.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}邪魔すぎる運命のターゲット睨みながら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:49.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,800)\blur2\be1}言えそうで良かった「まだ愛していたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:41.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}為錯位的焦點所惑 四下尋找說辭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:44.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}看吧枯葉起舞 終會化為蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}然後調節到位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:47.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,0)\blur2\be1}然後是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:51.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}時過境遷太急 秒速開始不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:53.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全因自己武斷的選擇開端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以必須做出了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:00:59.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}無聊的理由 是停止思考的鐵證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}無法守護應守護之物 那就不要亂出頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:08.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共鳴 榮光 稱讚 都不應奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:11.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不明真相的引力 將常識歸於虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:13.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}會扣下扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:18.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不是開玩笑的 幻覺已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:20.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,500)\blur2\be1}充滿謊言的海市蜃樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:23.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}讓心都變得模糊的海市蜃樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:26.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善善惡惡都無法評議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:30.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全都變得討厭 連這都是幸福的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:35.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不行 不要說得如此悲涼 世界依然活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:37.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}即使你會哭泣也還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:40.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以想看到這片天空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:45.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}一邊瞪視過於礙眼的命運的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:49.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,800)\blur2\be1}能說出口就好 “還想繼續愛”
